name: Global Token
description: GBL token is the lifeblood of WaweSwaps, fueling its liquidity enhancement mission. As a decentralized platform, WaweSwaps uses GBL to empower users, providing proportional token distribution and liquidity rewards. Built on the Binance Smart Chain, it employs an AMM mechanism for seamless token swaps and embraces a DAO voting model for user engagement. GBL's integral role ensures a user-centric, reliable, and dynamic cryptocurrency trading environment on WaweSwaps.
